  "body": "Hi, we have a problem with our Besu nodes, they run out of space after a while, they consume a lot of disk space. I have read somewhere that with the use of Merklee Trees it is possible to solve this issue. I have not found anything in the documentation about this issue, is it possible with Hyperledger Besu to work with this technology?\r\n\r\nThanks",
