    "body": "Hi, I think what you are searching is the `--Xdata-storage-format=BONSAI` argument. That's still an experimental feature and not recommended for production. You can find experimental/unstable features by usign the `--Xhelp` flag. You will need to do a complete resync if you want to try it.\r\n\r\nhttps://consensys.net/blog/news/bonsai-tries-a-big-update-for-small-state-storage-in-hyperledger-besu/",
